<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Rahil Malik | Portfolio</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f5f7fa;
color:#333;
line-height:1.6;
}

header{
background:#0f172a;
color:white;
padding:40px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

header img{
width:120px;
height:120px;
border-radius:50%;
object-fit:cover;
border:4px solid white;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

nav{
margin-top:15px;
}

nav a{
color:white;
margin:0 10px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

section{
padding:60px 20px;
max-width:1000px;
margin:auto;
}

h2{
margin-bottom:20px;
color:#0f172a;
}

.about p{
font-size:18px;
}

.skills{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(120px,1fr));
gap:15px;
}

.skill{
background:white;
padding:15px;
border-radius:8px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.timeline{
border-left:3px solid #0f172a;
padding-left:20px;
}

.timeline-item{
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.projects{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
}

.project-card{
background:white;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.project-card a{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:10px;
color:#2563eb;
text-decoration:none;
}

.contact{
text-align:center;
}

.contact a{
display:block;
margin:10px 0;
color:#2563eb;
text-decoration:none;
}

footer{
background:#0f172a;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
margin-top:40px;
}

@media(max-width:600px){
header{
padding:30px 15px;
}

section{
padding:40px 15px;
}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<img src="photo-placeholder.jpg" alt="Rahil Malik Photo">
<h1>Rahil Malik</h1>
<p>Entrepreneur | Handicraft Business Owner | Creative Thinker</p>

<nav>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#skills">Skills</a>
<a href="#experience">Experience</a>
<a href="#projects">Projects</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section id="about" class="about">
<h2>About Me</h2>
<p>
Hello, my name is <strong>Rahil Malik</strong>. I am passionate about business, creativity, and building unique products. 
I am involved in the handicraft industry and continuously work on developing creative ideas and business opportunities.
I enjoy learning new skills, growing my business, and connecting with people.
</p>
</section>

<section id="skills">
<h2>Skills</h2>

<div class="skills">
<div class="skill">Business Management</div>
<div class="skill">Handicraft Design</div>
<div class="skill">Creativity</div>
<div class="skill">Entrepreneurship</div>
<div class="skill">Communication</div>
<div class="skill">Marketing</div>
</div>

</section>

<section id="experience">
<h2>Experience</h2>

<div class="timeline">

<div class="timeline-item">
<h3>Handicraft Business</h3>
<p>Working in handicraft design and business development.</p>
</div>

<div class="timeline-item">
<h3>Entrepreneurship</h3>
<p>Managing and growing a personal business brand and exploring new market opportunities.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="projects">
<h2>Projects</h2>

<div class="projects">

<div class="project-card">
<h3>Handicraft Brand</h3>
<p>Development of a premium handicraft brand with creative handmade products.</p>
<a href="#">View Project</a>
</div>

<div class="project-card">
<h3>Portfolio Website</h3>
<p>A personal portfolio website to showcase projects, experience, and skills.</p>
<a href="#">View Project</a>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">
<h2>Contact</h2>

<p>Feel free to contact me for business or collaboration.</p>

<a href="#">Email: your-email@example.com</a>
<a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
<a href="#">Instagram</a>
<a href="#">Website</a>

</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Rahil Malik. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
